OL,3,CGail's to drop soya milk charge after
OL,4,CPeta campaign
OL,6,FPeta's Vice President of Vegan
OL,7,FCorporate Projects, Dawn Carr said:
OL,8,F"Charging more for plant milk leaves a
OL,9,Fbad taste in customers' mouths,
OL,10,Fparticularly when it is a choice they
OL,11,Fmake for their health, to be kind to
OL,12,Fcows, or for the planet.
OL,14,F"Peta celebrates Gail's taking the
OL,15,Ffirst step in offering soya without
OL,16,Fthe surcharge, but to spare cows from
OL,17,Fharm and reduce methane emissions, the
OL,18,Foat milk upcharge also has to be
OL,19,Fground down."
