OL,3,CGail's to drop soya milk charge after
OL,4,CPeta campaign
OL,6,FAccording to the Association of UK
OL,7,FDietitians, demand for plant-based
OL,8,Fmilks is on the rise, with around one
OL,9,Fin three people in the UK now drinking
OL,10,Fplant-based alternatives.
OL,12,FAround 12% of people said they did so
OL,13,Fbecause of the ill-treatment of cows
OL,14,Fin the production of dairy products.
OL,16,FGail's joins Cafe Nero, Costa and
OL,17,Fothers that offer at least one dairy-
OL,18,Ffree milk without an added charge,
OL,19,Fwhile Starbucks, Pret, Leon and Joe
OL,20,Fand the Juice have stopped charging
OL,21,Ffor all vegan milk alternatives.
